    Detailed Description

    template<class K, class V>
    class oos::factory< K, V >

    A generic factory class.

    Template Parameters
    KThe type for the key value.
    VThe value type.

    This is a generic factory class where values are stored in producer objects as pointers wrapped by std::shared_ptr of type V. The key type is used to identify the producer. Once create is called a new serializable of value type V is created and returned. The class uses a producer interface of type producer_base and a defualt producer class default_producer is provided.

    This is a generic factory class where values are stored in producer objects as pointers wrapped by std::shared_ptr of type V. The key type is used to identify the producer. Once create is called a new serializable of value type V is created and returned. The class uses a producer interface of type producer_base and a defualt producer class default_producer is provided.
